EchoMind is an AI-powered meeting summarizer designed to transform hours of conversations into actionable insights within minutes.
It combines the power of Whisper.cpp for accurate speech-to-text conversion and Ollama for advanced text summarization â€” all wrapped in a user-friendly Gradio interface.

Built to enhance productivity and collaboration, EchoMind integrates seamlessly with platforms like Zoom, Google Meet, and Microsoft Teams via Recall.ai, ensuring every voice is captured, identified, and remembered.

ðŸ’¡ Key Highlights:

Converts meeting audio into text using Whisper.cpp

Generates concise, human-like summaries using LLMs via Ollama

Supports multiple models and languages

Provides speaker diarization for clarity on who said what

Built with a minimal and interactive Gradio interface

Ideal for teams, educators, and professionals who need quick meeting recaps
